about.summary: The GraphQL frontend to python dagster.

name: dagster_graphql
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "dagster_graphql" %}
{% set version = "0.6.4" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 6be08e5bb411288a2bf60ac5a4a5ef3ced189ef95d3991395100a6449d016da8

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - dagster-graphql = dagster_graphql.cli:main
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - gevent 1.3.7.*
    - gevent-websocket 0.10.1.*
    - graphene >=2.1.3
    - requests
    - dagster {{ version }}.*

test:
  imports:
    - dagster_graphql
    - dagster_graphql.client
    - dagster_graphql.schema
  commands:
    - dagster-graphql --help

about:
  home: "https://github.com/dagster-io/dagster/tree/master/python_modules/dagster-graphql"
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "The GraphQL frontend to python dagster."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - xhochy
